{
  "stem": "4693.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They let you to fall asleep for half an hour, and they call you out again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they found photos of me, so they wanted to know who this person is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And still, really very same questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Said I was a spy, and what have you, and-- Then from jail, one night, I was called out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all were called out, one by one, and we were read our sentences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would put so-called-- Russian system was called [RUSSIAN]-- special commission of three.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which supposedly was-- what they were doing, they had a stamp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One would stamp three years, one stamp five years, one eight, one 10.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one was-- and certain percentage got three, certain percentage got five, certain eight, certain 10.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got three.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there were taken to Kharkiv to a special jail, which was a transport jail, from which they would send later to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until then, we were kept completely separate from Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Kharkiv, by mistake, they put two Russians in with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw one of them had a face, a very prominent face, of a very intelligent guy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the cell, where we are 200 in a cell, which was a bit bigger than these two rooms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were lying by night later, we had to lie like sardines-- in the nude, one into the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I moved to this guy somewhere, and I started talking to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the most intelligent, the brightest guy I ever met in my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Has had a very interesting story, he was early communist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the early '20s, he got disillusioned with the communism, and he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with the help of his friends, who were all of high positions from his party, he escaped.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
